data.description: LOW HOA and ready for FHA and totally perfect for a first time home buyer, starter home! This home sits in a very quiet, well kept, community in Western Lake, in The subdivision of suburban Pines, beautifully tucked away off Malaleuca Rd. It has it's own private community clubhouse, pool and park like green space. This large Townhouse has a bedroom and half bathroom downstairs and two full bedrooms and bathroom upstairs, with an outdoor grill, large patio, and plenty of room for patio furniture! Park right outside your gated entrance! Enjoy the sunsets from your balcony!
